snippet.title: Days Of Night Official Trailer
snippet.description:
GAME LINK IN BIO!!!!!

Your freshly 18 and seeking experience in the work force. You struggle to find work until one day the opportunity of a life time would come your way.

Little to you're knowledge you would be stepping in a world of HORROR!

Experience the HORRORS of working night shift at you're local grocery store.
